name: No forest, no life
description:
Reasons to stop the world destruction?
No forest, no life

### This piece was made to support our forest protectors. Thousands of people are mobilizing against Brazilian genocidal policies towards our first nations.

We can't watch all our forest turn into desert. 

All sales will go to tz1hEvcPQt2ku6J4c5V8DcLhBbuSjj53iUxD to suport the fight.

Help stop the indigenous genocide in Brazil.
